snippet.title: Old Tower for Commodore 64
snippet.description:
GRAB YOU COPY AT:
https://retrosouls.itch.io/old-tower-commodore-64

You play as a little explorers in a towers full of deadly traps and ugly batz. Your only weapons to help you win: quick-thinking and skill.

OLD TOWER  is programmed with KickAsm after a six years break. It's FREE or pay what your want. 

Download contains PRG+TAP file.

Have Fun!

Feel free to check out music mate souncloud at send him some love vibes: https://soundcloud.com/n1k-o/sets/segaoldtowers-ost


RetroSouls Team 2018-2020
www.retrosouls.net
